{
  "video_id": "iqEHuB-T2qQ",
  "title": "How I turned a deadly plant into a thriving business | Achenyo Idachaba",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12880.0,
      "end_time": 15960.0,
      "text": "Welcome to Bayeku,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15120.0,
      "end_time": 18496.0,
      "text": "a riverine community in Ikorodu, Lagos --"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18520.0,
      "end_time": 24896.0,
      "text": "a vivid representation of several riverine communities across Nigeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24920.0,
      "end_time": 28896.0,
      "text": "communities whose waterways have been infested"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28920.0,
      "end_time": 31776.0,
      "text": "by an invasive aquatic weed;"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31800.0,
      "end_time": 37560.0,
      "text": "communities where economic livelihoods have been hampered:"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37800.0,
      "end_time": 40296.0,
      "text": "fishing, marine transportation"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40320.0,
      "end_time": 41576.0,
      "text": "and trading;"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41600.0,
      "end_time": 45776.0,
      "text": "communities where fish yields have diminished;"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45800.0,
      "end_time": 50416.0,
      "text": "communities where schoolchildren are unable to go to school"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50440.0,
      "end_time": 54736.0,
      "text": "for days, sometimes weeks, on end."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54760.0,
      "end_time": 57616.0,
      "text": "Who would have thought that this plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 57640.0,
      "end_time": 64376.0,
      "text": "with round leaves, inflated stems, and showy, lavender flowers"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 64400.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68176.0,
      "text": "would cause such havoc in these communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 68200.0,
      "end_time": 70976.0,
      "text": "The plant is known as water hyacinth"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 71000.0,
      "end_time": 74296.0,
      "text": "and its botanical name, Eichhornia crassipes."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 74320.0,
      "end_time": 78856.0,
      "text": "Interestingly, in Nigeria, the plant is also known by other names,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78880.0,
      "end_time": 81735.0,
      "text": "names associated with historical events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 81760.0,
      "end_time": 83656.0,
      "text": "as well as myths."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 83680.0,
      "end_time": 87776.0,
      "text": "In some places, the plant is called Babangida."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87800.0,
      "end_time": 92936.0,
      "text": "When you hear Babangida, you remember the military and military coups."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 92960.0,
      "end_time": 96295.0,
      "text": "And you think: fear, restraint."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 96320.0,
      "end_time": 101696.0,
      "text": "In parts of Nigeria in the Niger Delta, the plant is also known as Abiola."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 101720.0,
      "end_time": 106136.0,
      "text": "When you hear Abiola, you remember annulled elections"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 106160.0,
      "end_time": 108776.0,
      "text": "and you think: dashed hopes."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 108800.0,
      "end_time": 111336.0,
      "text": "In the southwestern part of Nigeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 111360.0,
      "end_time": 113576.0,
      "text": "the plant is known as Gbe&#39;borun."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 113600.0,
      "end_time": 115375.0,
      "text": "Gbe&#39;borun is a Yoruba phrase"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 115400.0,
      "end_time": 119376.0,
      "text": "which translates to \"gossip,\" or \"talebearer.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 119400.0,
      "end_time": 125216.0,
      "text": "When you think of gossip, you think: rapid reproduction, destruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 125240.0,
      "end_time": 127776.0,
      "text": "And in the Igala-speaking part of Nigeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 127800.0,
      "end_time": 130656.0,
      "text": "the plant is known as A Kp&#39;iye Kp&#39;oma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 130680.0,
      "end_time": 133376.0,
      "text": "And when you hear that, you think of death."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 133400.0,
      "end_time": 138256.0,
      "text": "It literally translates to \"death to mother and child.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 138280.0,
      "end_time": 143136.0,
      "text": "I personally had my encounter with this plant in the year 2009."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143160.0,
      "end_time": 148896.0,
      "text": "It was shortly after I had relocated from the US to Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 148920.0,
      "end_time": 151456.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d quit my job in corporate America"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 151480.0,
      "end_time": 154655.0,
      "text": "and decided to take this big leap of faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 154680.0,
      "end_time": 158176.0,
      "text": "a leap of faith that came out of a deep sense of conviction"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 158200.0,
      "end_time": 160335.0,
      "text": "that there was a lot of work to do in Nigeria"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 160360.0,
      "end_time": 162816.0,
      "text": "in the area of sustainable development."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 162840.0,
      "end_time": 165816.0,
      "text": "And so here I was in the year 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 165840.0,
      "end_time": 167976.0,
      "text": "actually, at the end of 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 168000.0,
      "end_time": 171160.0,
      "text": "in Lagos on the Third Mainland Bridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 171400.0,
      "end_time": 175696.0,
      "text": "And I looked to my left and saw this very arresting image."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 175720.0,
      "end_time": 177496.0,
      "text": "It was an image of fishing boats"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 177520.0,
      "end_time": 183256.0,
      "text": "that had been hemmed in by dense mats of water hyacinth."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 183280.0,
      "end_time": 185656.0,
      "text": "And I was really pained by what I saw"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 185680.0,
      "end_time": 187176.0,
      "text": "because I thought to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 187200.0,
      "end_time": 189550.0,
      "text": "\"These poor fisherfolk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 189800.0,
      "end_time": 193936.0,
      "text": "how are they going to go about their daily activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 193960.0,
      "end_time": 196560.0,
      "text": "with these restrictions.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 196800.0,
      "end_time": 199136.0,
      "text": "And then I thought, \"There&#39;s got to be a better way.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 199160.0,
      "end_time": 204176.0,
      "text": "A win-win solution whereby the environment is taken care of"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 204200.0,
      "end_time": 206576.0,
      "text": "by the weeds being cleared out of the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 206600.0,
      "end_time": 209736.0,
      "text": "and then this being turned into an economic benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 209760.0,
      "end_time": 212576.0,
      "text": "for the communities whose lives are impacted the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 212600.0,
      "end_time": 214359.0,
      "text": "by the infestation of the weed."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 215160.0,
      "end_time": 218736.0,
      "text": "That, I would say, was my spark moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 218760.0,
      "end_time": 222215.0,
      "text": "And so I did further research to find out more"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 222240.0,
      "end_time": 225176.0,
      "text": "about the beneficial uses of this weed."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 225200.0,
      "end_time": 228616.0,
      "text": "Out of the several, one struck me the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 228640.0,
      "end_time": 231736.0,
      "text": "It was the use of the plant for handicrafts."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 231760.0,
      "end_time": 234960.0,
      "text": "And I thought, \"What a great idea.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 234120.0,
      "end_time": 236496.0,
      "text": "Personally, I love handicrafts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 236520.0,
      "end_time": 241176.0,
      "text": "especially handicrafts that are woven around a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 241200.0,
      "end_time": 245815.0,
      "text": "And so I thought, \"This could be easily deployed within the communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 245840.0,
      "end_time": 249376.0,
      "text": "without the requirement of technical skills.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 249400.0,
      "end_time": 254400.0,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, \"Three simple steps to a mega solution.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 255400.0,
      "end_time": 260135.0,
      "text": "First step: Get out into the waterways and harvest the water hyacinth."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 260160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262456.0,
      "text": "That way, you create access."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 262480.0,
      "end_time": 267560.0,
      "text": "Secondly, you dry the water hyacinth stems."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 267800.0,
      "end_time": 272495.0,
      "text": "And thirdly, you weave the water hyacinth into products."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 272519.0,
      "end_time": 274896.0,
      "text": "The third step was a challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 274920.0,
      "end_time": 277616.0,
      "text": "See, I&#39;m a computer scientist by background"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 277640.0,
      "end_time": 280296.0,
      "text": "and not someone in the creative arts."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 280320.0,
      "end_time": 282160.0,
      "text": "And so I began my quest"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 282400.0,
      "end_time": 284976.0,
      "text": "to find out how I can learn how to weave."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 285000.0,
      "end_time": 289136.0,
      "text": "And this quest took me to a community in Ibadan, where I lived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 289160.0,
      "end_time": 290576.0,
      "text": "called Sabo."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 290600.0,
      "end_time": 293456.0,
      "text": "Sabo translates to \"strangers&#39; quarters.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 293480.0,
      "end_time": 296496.0,
      "text": "And the community is predominantly made up of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 296520.0,
      "end_time": 298496.0,
      "text": "from the northern part of the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 298520.0,
      "end_time": 301455.0,
      "text": "So I literally took my dried weeds in hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 301480.0,
      "end_time": 303560.0,
      "text": "there were several more of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 303800.0,
      "end_time": 306416.0,
      "text": "and went knocking from door to door to find out who could teach me"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 306440.0,
      "end_time": 310856.0,
      "text": "how to weave these water hyacinth stems into ropes."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 310880.0,
      "end_time": 314000.0,
      "text": "And I was directed to the shed of Malam Yahaya."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 314880.0,
      "end_time": 317896.0,
      "text": "The problem, though, is that Malam Yahaya doesn&#39;t speak English"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 317920.0,
      "end_time": 320160.0,
      "text": "and neither did I speak Hausa."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 320400.0,
      "end_time": 322176.0,
      "text": "But some little kids came to the rescue"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 322200.0,
      "end_time": 323976.0,
      "text": "and helped translate."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 324000.0,
      "end_time": 327256.0,
      "text": "And that began my journey of learning how to weave"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 327280.0,
      "end_time": 331856.0,
      "text": "and transform these dried water hyacinth stems"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 331880.0,
      "end_time": 334760.0,
      "text": "into long ropes."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 335400.0,
      "end_time": 337655.0,
      "text": "With my long ropes in hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 337680.0,
      "end_time": 340776.0,
      "text": "I was now equipped to make products."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 340800.0,
      "end_time": 343216.0,
      "text": "And that was the beginning of partnerships."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 343240.0,
      "end_time": 347216.0,
      "text": "Working with rattan basket makers to come up with products."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 347240.0,
      "end_time": 350160.0,
      "text": "So with this in hand, I felt confident"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 350400.0,
      "end_time": 352400.0,
      "text": "that I would be able to take this knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 352640.0,
      "end_time": 354616.0,
      "text": "back into the riverine communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 354640.0,
      "end_time": 359895.0,
      "text": "and help them to transform their adversity into prosperity."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 359920.0,
      "end_time": 363960.0,
      "text": "So taking these weeds and actually weaving them"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 363120.0,
      "end_time": 365696.0,
      "text": "into products that can be sold."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 365720.0,
      "end_time": 369456.0,
      "text": "So we have pens, we have tableware,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 369480.0,
      "end_time": 373256.0,
      "text": "we have purses, we have tissue boxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 373280.0,
      "end_time": 375816.0,
      "text": "Thereby, helping the communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 375840.0,
      "end_time": 379150.0,
      "text": "to see water hyacinth in a different light."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 379400.0,
      "end_time": 381696.0,
      "text": "Seeing water hyacinth as being valuable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 381720.0,
      "end_time": 387856.0,
      "text": "being aesthetic, being durable, tough, resilient."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 387880.0,
      "end_time": 391256.0,
      "text": "Changing names, changing livelihoods."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 391280.0,
      "end_time": 394256.0,
      "text": "From Gbe&#39;borun, gossip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 394280.0,
      "end_time": 397950.0,
      "text": "to Olusotan, storyteller."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 397120.0,
      "end_time": 401136.0,
      "text": "And from A Kp&#39;iye Kp&#39;oma, which is \"killer of mother and child,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 401160.0,
      "end_time": 403496.0,
      "text": "to Ya du j&#39;ewn w&#39;Iye kp&#39;Oma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 403520.0,
      "end_time": 406895.0,
      "text": "\"provider of food for mother and child.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 406920.0,
      "end_time": 410776.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d like to end with a quote by Michael Margolis."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 410800.0,
      "end_time": 415816.0,
      "text": "He said, \"If you want to learn about a culture, listen to the stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 415840.0,
      "end_time": 419895.0,
      "text": "And if you want to change a culture, change the stories.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 419920.0,
      "end_time": 425160.0,
      "text": "And so, from Makoko community, to Abobiri, to Ewoi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 425400.0,
      "end_time": 428696.0,
      "text": "to Kolo, to Owahwa, Esaba,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 428720.0,
      "end_time": 431296.0,
      "text": "we have changed the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 431320.0,
      "end_time": 432856.0,
      "text": "Thank you for listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 432880.0,
      "end_time": 436000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}